---
// Beyond Work Section (Asymmetric Magazine Layout)
---

<section id="beyond-work" class="beyond-work">
  <div class="sticky-header">
    <div class="section-header fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="section-title">Beyond Work</h2>
      <p>审美与能量的来源</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="magazine-grid">
    <!-- Aesthetics (Photography/Art) -->
    <div class="grid-item aesthetics fade-in-up">
      <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder liquid-glass">
        <!-- Image placeholder -->
      </div>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Lens & Canvas</h3>
        <p>捕捉光线与构图的平衡。长期的视觉训练让我对克制感、材质与排版更敏感，这直接影响了我对产品体验的判断。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Energy (Running/Cycling) -->
    <div class="grid-item energy fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
      <div class="text-block liquid-glass">
        <h3>100km & 800m</h3>
        <p>
          曾把共享单车从紫金港骑到海宁（100公里），也拿过校运会800米冠军。
          运动对我来说不是“标签”，而是一种建立耐心、输出稳定性的长期主义训练。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image-wrapper small bg-placeholder liquid-glass mt-sm">
        <!-- Image placeholder -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .beyond-work {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sticky-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--header-height);
    z-index: 10;
    /* Optional slight background blur so text is readable over scrolling images */
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-bg) 60%, transparent);
    margin: 0 calc(var(--space-md) * -1); /* Pull out to edge to cover */
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-title {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .magazine-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center; /* Asymmetric alignment */
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover, .text-block:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
    box-shadow: 
      inset 0 1px 1px var(--color-glass-highlight),
      inset 0 0 0 1px var(--color-glass-edge),
      0 12px 24px var(--color-glass-shadow),
      0 24px 48px var(--color-glass-shadow-deep);
  }

  .image-wrapper.small {
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    width: 80%;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .caption, .text-block {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .text-block {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .magazine-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
    
    .image-wrapper.small {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
